            "text": "but the need for a highly differentiated content \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "specialized to promote optimal learning for each unique learner . <S>\r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "To address this synthesis problem \r",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "we have developed a generative platform \r",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "capable of dynamically varying content \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "based on the individual student needs . <S>\r",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "This approach recently achieved 93 % mastery of a key algebra concept even for primary school students in three state-wide challenges . <S>\r",
            "relation": "EVALUATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "In this talk I will describe our work on extending the platform \r",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
